          Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and React.
        </p>
        <div class="row mt-4">
          <div class="col-6">
            <div class="about-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">Name:</span>
              <span>R. Durgadevi</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">City:</span>
              <span>Madurai</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">Degree:</span>
              <span>msc</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-6">
            <div class="about-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">Email:</span>
              <span>zoyadeveloper1@gmail.com</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">Freelance:</span>
              <span>Available</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">Status:</span>
              <span>Intern @ Cognifyz</span>
